{"tid":542811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無泊到200呎樓碼頭!]17歲DSE考生　墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-01-27T23:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T00:38:24.000Z","uid":65346,"like":9,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"11feb404bfe4634751a56432d0ba732c839c77cc","tid":542811,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T23:52:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180128/20288190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F20288190&d=a0EL2TqwfpJ7CvUbxbS21smB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=32ec7227\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180128%2F20288190&h=583eeed0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180128/20288190</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名DSE考生墮樓亡！前晚10時許，葵涌葵盛東邨，一名姓陳17歲少女從高處墮下，倒臥盛逸樓對開，重傷昏迷。救護人員接報趕到將事主送院搶救，惜終告不治。警方在停車場五樓平台發現一對拖鞋，相信她由該處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，女事主是一名中六女生，在青衣一間中間讀書，成續名列前茅，是應屆DSE考生，疑考試壓力困擾，加上事發前與家人爭執。警方於現場沒有撿獲遺書，調查事件沒有可疑。<br />\n<br />\n街坊稱，死者與父母及胞姐同住，父親任職超市司機，母親為家庭主婦，間日做兼職；胞姐則在區內工作。"},{"pid":"fbd3ad8932d5150b2a8713787921d0c59c24de84","tid":542811,"uid":97814,"like":4,"dislike":25,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T23:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"582c25eb921248b1830d07b02e8ffcd25d002c74","tid":542811,"uid":29314,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T00:09:43.000Z","msg":"佢老豆超市司機！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n輸在起跑線啦！"},{"pid":"895f56b599cf5c53b5f49e9fffcfcbf24ef2e6fb","tid":542811,"uid":111006,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T00:10:46.000Z","msg":"發覺好多自殺學生都係住屋邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ef00450260bd16defd65fd43edf56203a5a9ce","tid":542811,"uid":123605,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"re